defaultSRdefault2default: Buy in bulk to achieve the best value from the market.default&#xa0;
defaultScape uses a tried and tested process that drives out waste and make clients work more efficiently.  This can take time and involves some training but can achieve substantial savings.  North Somerset Council use Scape and have achieved a 75% improvement in productivity and £2.4m savings in two years. 
default&#xa0;
defaultScape have a robust and very efficient engagement / 
defaultproject delivery process which minimises unproductive costs and takes waste, in the form of unproductive duplication, out of the system. The Scape process develops design and project delivery solutions in collaboration with the client and 
defaultensures an 
defaultintegrated delivery team. 
